REST API - Representational State Transfer

Http  Methods - CRUD Operations

GET - Read    @GetMapping
    
POST - Create @PostMapping

PUT - Replace @PutMapping


PATCH - Update @PatchMapping

DELETE - Remove @DeleteMapping


      JSON - Postman

{
   "timestamp" : "2026-02-01"
   "status" : 200
   "error" : "Validation failed"
}

Status Code :

200 - OK Success (GET)
201 - Created - (POST)
204 - No content - success, no body (PUT/DELETE)

400 - Bad Request
401 - Unauthorized
403 - forbidden
404 - not found
409 - version confilcts
422, 429 - Too many request

500 -Internal server error 
